", "hashtagName": "islam", "type": 1, "subType": 0, "isCommerce": false}, {"awemeId": "", "start": 640, "end": 649, "hashtagId": "4210139", "hashtagName": "musulman", "type": 1, "subType": 0, "isCommerce": false}, {"awemeId": "", "start": 650, "end": 657, "hashtagId": "6497450", "hashtagName": "rappel", "type": 1, "subType": 0, "isCommerce": false}, {"awemeId": "", "start": 658, "end": 669, "hashtagId": "4463184", "hashtagName": "invocation", "type": 1, "subType": 0, "isCommerce": false}], "secret": false, "forFriend": false, "digged": false, "itemCommentStatus": 0, "takeDown": 0, "effectStickers": [], "authorStats": {"followerCount": 2541, "followingCount": 57, "heart": 93900, "heartCount": 93900, "videoCount": 185, "diggCount": 1019, "friendCount": 0}, "privateItem": false, "duetEnabled": true, "stitchEnabled": true, "stickersOnItem": [{"stickerText": ["\ud83d\udc49 La prosternation : un \nmoment d\u2019invocation \ud83e\udd32\ud83c\udffd"], "stickerType": 9}], "isAd": false, "shareEnabled": true, "comments": [], "duetDisplay": 0, "stitchDisplay": 0, "indexEnabled": true, "locationCreated": "FR", "suggestedWords": [], "contents": [{"desc": "\ud83d\udc49 Dans la prosternation, le serviteur est au plus proche d\u2019Allah\u261d\ud83c\udffe", "textExtra": []}, {"desc": "Cheikh S\u00e2lih Ibn Al-\u2018Outheymine (rahimahouLl\u00e2h) rappelle qu\u2019il est permis d\u2019invoquer Allah pour les affaires de la dounya et de l\u2019au-del\u00e0, m\u00eame dans les pri\u00e8res obligatoires.", "textExtra": []}, {"desc": "Car l\u2019invocation, en elle-m\u00eame, est une adoration.", "textExtra": []}, {"desc": "", "textExtra": []}, {"desc": "\u26a0\ufe0f Profitons-en donc pour Lui confier nos besoins, nos espoirs et nos demandes, ici-bas et dans l\u2019au-del\u00e0 \ud83d\ude4c\ud83c\udffb", "textExtra": []}, {"desc": "", "textExtra": []}, {"desc": "\ud83d\udde3\ufe0f Le Proph\u00e8te \ufdfa a dit : \u00ab Celui qui montre un bien \u00e0 la m\u00eame r\u00e9compense que celui qui l'a fait \u00bb [Muslim 1893]\ud83c\udf38\ud83c\udf3f", "textExtra": []}, {"desc": "\ud83d\udce4 Abonne-toi et partage ce rappel sans mod\u00e9ration pour en faire b\u00e9n\u00e9ficier ton entourage \ud83d\udc65", "textExtra": []}, {"desc": ".", "textExtra": []}, {"desc": ".", "textExtra": []}, {"desc": ".", "textExtra": []}, {"desc": ".", "textExtra": []}, {"desc": "#pourtoi #islam #musulman #rappel #invocation ", "textExtra": [{"awemeId": "", "start": 0, "end": 8, "hashtagId": "2852101", "hashtagName": "pourtoi", "type": 1, "subType": 0, "isCommerce": false}, {"awemeId": "", "start": 9, "end": 15, "hashtagId": "350677", "hashtagName": "islam", "type": 1, "subType": 0, "isCommerce": false}, {"awemeId": "", "start": 16, "end": 25, "hashtagId": "4210139", "hashtagName": "musulman", "type": 1, "subType": 0, "isCommerce": false}, {"awemeId": "", "start": 26, "end": 33, "hashtagId": "6497450", "hashtagName": "rappel", "type": 1, "subType": 0, "isCommerce": false}, {"awemeId": "", "start": 34, "end": 45, "hashtagId": "4463184", "hashtagName": "invocation", "type": 1, "subType": 0, "isCommerce": false}]}], "diversificationId": 10083, "collected": false, "channelTags": [], "item_control": {"can_repost": true}, "IsAigc": false, "AIGCDescription": "", "backendSourceEventTracking": "", "CategoryType": 120, "textLanguage": "fr", "textTranslatable": true, "authorStatsV2": {"followerCount": "2541", "followingCount": "57", "heart": "93900", "heartCount": "93900", "videoCount": "185", "diggCount": "1019", "friendCount": "0"}, "isReviewing": false, "creatorAIComment": {"hasAITopic": false, "categoryList": [], "eligibleVideo": false, "notEligibleReason": 101}}}, "shareMeta": {"title": "be.muslim6 on TikTok", "desc": "\ud83d\udc49 Dans la prosternation, le serviteur est au plus proche d\u2019Allah\u261d\ud83c\udffe Cheikh S\u00e2lih Ibn Al-\u2018Outheymine (rahimahouLl\u00e2h) rappelle qu\u2019il est permis d\u2019invoquer Allah pour les affaires de la dounya et de l\u2019au-del\u00e0, m\u00eame dans les pri\u00e8res obligatoires. Car l\u2019invocation, en elle-m\u00eame, est une adoration. \u26a0\ufe0f Profitons-en donc pour Lui confier nos besoins, nos espoirs et nos demandes, ici-bas et dans l\u2019au-del\u00e0 \ud83d\ude4c\ud83c\udffb \ud83d\udde3\ufe0f Le Proph\u00e8te \ufdfa a dit : \u00ab Celui qui montre un bien \u00e0 la m\u00eame r\u00e9compense que celui qui l'a fait \u00bb [Muslim 1893]\ud83c\udf38\ud83c\udf3f \ud83d\udce4 Abonne-toi et partage ce rappel sans mod\u00e9ration pour en faire b\u00e9n\u00e9ficier ton entourage \ud83d\udc65 . . . . #pourtoi #islam #musulman #rappel #invocation "}, "statusCode": 0, "statusMsg": ""}